# üëã CRAFT: Concept Recursive Activation FacTorization for Explainability (CVPR 2023)

This repository contains code for the paper:

*CRAFT: Concept Recursive Activation FacTorization for Explainability*, Thomas Fel*, Agustin Picard*, Louis Bethune*, Thibaut Boissin*, David Vigouroux, Julien Colin, R√©mi Cad√®ne, Thomas Serre. CVPR 2023, [[arXiv]](https://arxiv.org/abs/2211.10154).

The code is implemented and available **for Pytorch & Tensorflow**. A notebook for each of them is available: [notebook Pytorch](./craft_pytorch.ipynb), [notebook Tensorflow](./craft_tensorflow.ipynb).

